metadata.name: No.Use #1
metadata.description: from the hack artist OFF HVND, No.Use is a series of 9261 randomly generated skulls on the Ethereum blockchain. (OFF HVND isn't clever enough to come up some cool lore or whatever, so you can just make some up.) holding one of these stupid things will grant access to gated merch, physical rewards, and a community where you can all FUD projects together... your friends will be so jealous.
